      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "To save you the lookup - &quot;The HashMap class is roughly equivalent to Hashtable, except that it is unsynchronized and permits nulls.&quot; - Taken from the link in the answer - <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/util/HashMap.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/util/HashMap.html</a>"
